trend_summary: 2000-2020 imagery shows a mainly rural peninsula where built-up land remains sparse. Incremental housing lines the central highway, and the river-side industrial plant enlarges its footprint and storage yards. Several small fields transition to young forest, while other croplands are periodically cleared. Shoreline marsh extends slightly seaward, hinting at sediment build-up.
